 *
 *  @section installing_database_jessie Debian 8 "Jessie"
 *
 *  Run <code>apt-get install libsqlite3-dev</code> and/or <code>apt-get install libpqxx3-dev postgresql</code> as the
 *  administrator.
 *
 *  The "postgresql" package is required only if you wish to run the PostgreSQL server locally.
 *
 *  @section installing_database_ubuntu1404 Ubuntu 14.04 "Trusty Tahr"
 *
 *  Run <code>apt-get install libsqlite3-dev</code> and/or <code>apt-get install libpqxx3-dev postgresql</code> as the
 *  administrator.
 *
